      <section eId="sec_CCP-593">
        <num>CCP 593</num>
        <heading>593. Â Venue</heading>
        <subsection eId="CCP-593__subsec_A">
          <num>A.</num>
          <content>
            <p>An action brought on behalf of a class shall be brought in a parish of proper venue as to the defendant.</p>
          </content>
        </subsection>
        <subsection eId="CCP-593__subsec_B">
          <num>B.</num>
          <content>
            <p>An action brought against a class shall be brought in a parish of proper venue as to any member of the class named as a defendant.</p>
          </content>
        </subsection>
        <authorialNote marker="source">
          <p>Source: https://www.legis.la.gov/legis/Law.aspx?d=112186</p>
        </authorialNote>
      </section>
